const char gCompressedText_MSG_0903[] = "	QjYour Majesty, I bear bad news.\x03The castle gate has been breached.\x03Emperor Vigarde's forces are withinthe castle walls.\x03	I understand.\x03The garrison has fallen.\x03We've lost contact with Prince Ephraimand can expect no aid from his men.\x03Your Majesty, what are we to do?\x03	...What else can we do?\x03Order your men to laydown their arms.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_0904[] = "	Q\x13Father...\x03	Eirika.\x03Are you wearing thebracelet I gave you?\x03Yes, I have it right here.\x03	Good.\x03	Seth.\x03\x13\x13Yes, Your Majesty?\x03	Take Eirika and head for Frelia.\x03King Hayden is an honorable man.I trust he will keep you safe.\x03\x13Understood.\x03And what of Your Majesty?\x03	Me? I shall remain here.\x03We have long held Grado among ourdearest allies, yet now, they attack?\x03I must know why.\x03	Am I somehow responsible for this?Have I erred in my leadership?\x03Renais is mine to guide... Howcould I have failed her so?\x03\x13Father, you can't stay! You mustn't!\x03If you remain behind, then so shall I!\x03	Go now, Seth! Ride!Take her to safety!\x03";
