const char gCompressedText_MSG_0907[] = "		General Seth!\x03Franz, ride ahead and bring word of ourcoming to Frelia.\x03A single rider has better odds of passingunseen by Grado's men.\x03Convey to the throne all that has happenedhere and petition for reinforcements.\x03	U-understood!\x03";
