const char gCompressedText_MSG_0909[] = "\nBYou there, with the girl. Tell me, wouldthat be the wayward princess of Renais?\x03Well, this must be my lucky day.\x03You're a dead man. The wench goeswith me.\x03\nNever!\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_090A[] = "	B	I am Valter, the Moonstone,Grado's finest general!\x03And you're just a corpse whodoes not know he is dead.\x03";
