const char gCompressedText_MSG_090C[] = "BSuch terrible wounds, and stillhe holds to his duty?\x03How entertaining.\x03Fly away, little man. Fly away.Try to outrun death.\x03More time to savor the hunt...and the kill.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_090D[] = "		Princess Eirika! This way! I can see no more of Grado's men.\x03If we've made it this far, we'vesurely earned a moment's rest.\x03Please forgive my grabbing youso...brusquely earlier.\x03Don't be foolish, Seth.\x03If it weren't for you, I would neverhave made it out of the castle.\x03You are the reason I'm still alive.You have my gratitude.\x03\x13And whoever that man was, he wasclearly after me...\x03It's my fault that you receivedsuch a grave wound.\x03Allow me to treat it, I--\x03	Your Highness, I can't allow an injurylike this to be an obstacle.\x03We have more important matters toattend to. We must press on to Frelia.\x03We must fulfill His Majesty's wishes.\x03...\x03I wonder how my father fares alone inthe castle. Do you think he's safe?\x03And what of my brother on the Grado front?We've heard nothing from him for days.\x03	King Fado and Prince Ephraim areboth valiant and brave men.\x03I doubt even the might of the GradoEmpire can hold them in check.\x03More important to me, Your Highness, is that you look to your own safety.\x03How sad the two of them would be ifsomething were to happen to you.\x03We must reach Frelia to ensure theday of your happy reunion.\x03Yes, of course. You're right.\x03Until I'm reunited with my fatherand brother, I must not despair.\x03Come, Seth. Let us go.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_090E[] = "		Once we cross that bridge, we willbe in Frelia, near Border Mulan.\x03Let us proceed, Princess Eirika.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_090F[] = "	Your Highness, I won't lie to you.This will not be an easy ride.\x03Please, take this rapier.If something should happen to me,\x03you must continue to Frelia,alone if need be.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_0910[] = "0You there! Renais dogs! Wheredo you think you're going?\x03\nGrado's men...\x03Stand back, Princess Eirika.\x03\nIt's all right, Seth.\x03My brother has taught mesomething of swordplay.\x03I will stand with you.\x03";
