const char gCompressedText_MSG_0918[] = "		Princess, are you injured?\x03What?\x03Oh, no...I'm fine, Seth.\x03	But you look so pale...\x03I'm fine... Fine.\x03...This is war, isn't it?\x03It's not at all like the games I usedto play with my brother or Lyon.\x03I never thought-- I didn'tknow it would be this...savage.\x03Are words useless? Is strengthall that matters? It's so sad...\x03Why would the Grado Empire do this?To what end would they start a war?\x03	Princess...\x03...Don't worry, Seth. I won'tgive in to sorrow.\x03Let's get moving.\x03I'm not broken, and I won't stopuntil I see Renais restored.\x03I won't stop until I'm reunitedwith my father and brother.\x03";
