const char gCompressedText_MSG_0929[] = "	j,	Princess Tana! Grado'sforces are approaching!\x03What? So soon?Ah, we've had no time!\x03	Milady, we lack the arms to defend thisplace. You must return to Castle Frelia.\x03I can't! Not yet. We haven't foundEirika and her companions yet.\x03Eirika is my friend, and she needsmy help. I won't abandon her.\x03Oh, I know! Go and ask Father--I mean King Hayden for more troops.\x03	Yes, Your Highness!\x03	Eirika, please be safe.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_092A[] = "	k1	Commander Breguet, the enemy appears tobe fortifying its position in the castle.\x03Hmph.\x03They're tenacious, but they haveno hope of stopping our advance.\x03	What are your orders, sir?\x03Ha! Orders? You just stand here andwatch. I'll crush them myself!\x03	As you command, sir.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_092B[] = "	1	Ha! That's what happenswhen you face my lance!\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_092C[] = ",	1\x13St-stop right there!\x03Call off your forces and turn back,or you'll have me to deal with!\x03	Is that so? Andwho might you be?\x03Who--? I am Tana, Princessof Frelia.\x03I will not permit you to abusemy country any longer.\x03	Frelia's royal brat, huh?How convenient...\x03Leave this castle immediately.\x03If you harm me, my father and brotherwill chase you to the earth's end.\x03	Yes, I've heard how King Hayden doteson his precious little daughter.\x03Let's see how true that is. You'llmake us a fine hostage, my dear.\x03Seize the girl and lock her up!\x03\x13k\x13Right away, sir!\x03\x13No! Let me go!\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_092D[] = "	Seth, look...\x03	I see it. It seems like Grado'sarmy has already reached Frelia.\x03Princess, this place is perilous.\x03We should bypass Mulan altogetherand head straight to the castle.\x03But we can't just ignore this...\x03You were there when Renais wasinvaded... You saw what I saw.\x03You saw how the people suffered at the hands of Grado's soldiers.\x03Homes were destroyed, possessionsstolen, women kidnapped...\x03Anyone who resisted was executedwithout question, without hesitation.\x03	...\x03Please, Seth. I can't allow thatto happen here.\x03I don't want to see any more peopleharmed by Grado's atrocities.\x03	All right, Princess. I understand.Perhaps we can retake Mulan.\x03But, Princess, you must act withcaution. Your people need you, too.\x03Of course, Seth.Come on! Let's go!\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_092E[] = "Seth.\x03I need to know what's happening here.I'm going to visit that home.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_092F[] = "		Lady Eirika, what are your orders?\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_0930[] = "	1	Hm? Is that the princess of Renais?\x03Ha ha! It really is my lucky day!Fame and fortune ride to meet me!\x03Move on, you slugs!Bring that girl to me!\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_0931[] = "		Sir Gilliam, is that Mulan? Havewe reached Frelia's border already?\x03Aye, we have. Her Highness PrincessTana should be inside the castle.\x03	But look--the countryside iscrawling with Grado soldiers!\x03Where's the castle guard? HasMulan fallen? Are we too late?\x03Too tough to say from here.\x03Princess Tana's in no danger ifthey want her as a bargaining tool.\x03We men of the Eastern Watch willsee her to safety.\x03	Yes... Yes, of course.We mustn't give up. We must move.\x03We must retake the castle. Then, weride forth to Princess Eirika's aid.\x03I've stronger armor than you do.I'll take the lead. Watch my back.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_0932[] = "	Thanks, lad.\x03	Please, sir...\x03When I was a raw recruit, GeneralSeth taught me something.\x03He said every soldier can serve arole, even the most inexperienced.\x03Wait...\x03What is it?\x03	That knight... Is that General Seth?And his companion...must be Lady Eirika!\x03";
