const char gCompressedText_MSG_0937[] = "	,Princess Tana.\x03	Sir Gilliam...\x03I'm sorry. I never meantto cause you such trouble.\x03It was no trouble. I liveto serve, Princess.\x03\x13Tana!\x03	...Eirika?!?\x03Is that really you?\x03\x13Tana, what are you doing,so far from Castle Frelia?\x03	I heard that Renais had fallen,and I was so worried...\x03But I'm glad to see thatyou're safe...\x03Wait! Where is Ephraim?Is he well?\x03\x13I wish I knew.\x03	You haven't heard from him? Oh, I hope he's not been harmed...\x03Come, we must go to Castle Frelia.My lord father may know something.\x03\x13Thank you, Tana.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_0938[] = ",	Eirika!\x03Tana!? What areyou doing here?\x03	I heard that Renais had fallen,and I was so worried...\x03I'm so happy to see you're safe.\x03\x13\x13" "And it's our great pleasure to seethat you are well yourself, Lady Tana.\x03	Seth! You're all right!\x03Wait! Where is Ephraim?Is he well?\x03I wish I knew.\x03\x13We still have no word of Lord Ephraim.\x03	You haven't heard from him? Oh, Ihope he's not been harmed...\x03Come, we must go to Castle Frelia.My lord father may know something.\x03Thank you, Tana.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_0939[] = "		Princess Eirika, it is goodto see you're well.\x03Franz, you made it through unscathed...\x03	Y-yes, Your Highness!\x03I met up with Sir Gilliam of Freliaand explained the situation in Renais.\x03He told me that Princess Tana wasin danger as well, here at Mulan.\x03We rode as swiftly as we could.\x03Tana is here?\x03Franz, we must hurry!\x03	Understood!\x03";
