const char gCompressedText_MSG_0962[] = "\nYou saved my son.I owe you my thanks.\x03It's not necessary...\x03\n...Hold on a moment...\x03Aren't you...the great Garcia?You fought for Renais, didn't you?\x03......\x03Seth, do you know this man?\x03\nHe was a troop commander for Renaisuntil around ten years ago.\x03When I was a recruit, the soldiersused to tell so many tales about him.\x03They called him a daring and fearlessfighter for Renais.\x03Master Garcia, you must know the perilour homeland faces right now...\x03Can we impose upon you to lend yourstrength to Renais once again?\x03...I'm sorry. I'm retired now.\x03I'm not a soldier anymore. It's...a decision I made long ago.\x03\nMaster Garcia...\x03...When I was a soldier, I lived mylife fighting for my country's honor.\x03I left no time for my family.\x03I spent my life fighting for faceless,uncaring nobles.\x03When my wife fell ill and died, I metthe child she had left behind...\x03At that moment, I finally realizedwhat my duty had cost me.\x03......\x03I stood at my wife's grave and promisedher I would be a father to our son.\x03I'm done with armies. I'm done withfighting, except to protect my son.\x03I've no regrets. I'm the boy's father.\x03\n......\x03	\n	You...you blasted fool!\x03Father, what's all thisnonsense I'm hearing?\x03Ross!\x03	If you're not going, then I will!\x03I'm a fighter!I know I can do this!\x03\x13Ross, what are you saying?I...\x03	Dad, please! Listen to me!\x03I respect you more than anyother man in the world.\x03I know you gave up being asoldier for me. I know that!\x03But how can you throw awaysuch a big part of yourself?\x03You're a warrior at heart! You can't give that up and be happy!\x03......\x03	Look at me, Dad!Have you seen me fight?\x03I'm not a child anymore.I'm a warrior, like you.\x03You're free to worry, but I can survive on my own!\x03...Ross.\x03		You want to challenge me, Father?\x03I'm a fighter! The best in all of Ide!\x03I'm not gonna lose to you!I'm not gonna lose to anyone!\x03...You're right.\x03You're a good soldier, Ross.\x03	\nSir Seth...\x03If these old bones of mine canstill serve, I'd like to join you.\x03\x13	\x13" "Dad...\x03Looks like my boy grew up whileI wasn't looking...\x03He's tougher than I thought.He doesn't need my help.\x03I've raised him as best I could, but he's right.\x03I've nothing to fear. I should fight. I will fight.\x03\x13" "Dad!\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_0963[] = "	XThank you so much for your help.Please, stay the night and rest...\x03	We would if we could, but we havemuch to do and far to travel.\x03Your safety is reward enough.\x03Ah, well...\x03My, that is a splendidbracelet you're wearing.\x03	Thank you. My fathergave this to me.\x03It's a wonderful gift.\x03But you should be careful, wearingsuch a valuable item so openly.\x03Since Renais was invaded, things havebecome so dangerous around here.\x03There are gold-hungry thieves andbandits everywhere.\x03The most wicked are Bazba's Bandits.They are...cruel beyond words.\x03If you have something they want, yourlife is worth less than nothing.\x03Just the other day they assaulted sometravelers and... Oh, it was awful.\x03	I...I can't believe such things...\x03Oh, Renais is finished, mark my words.The Grado Empire's stolen our future.\x03Our only hope against them was thatPrince Ephraim would prevail, but...\x03Rumor has it that he's on the verge ofbeing crushed by Grado's vast numbers.\x03These are dark days. Travel with care.\x03	......\x03";
