const char gCompressedText_MSG_0965[] = "	.-	It's time to start.Are you ready, Eirika?\x03Yes, Ephraim.Let's begin.\x03	Tell me, though: why do you wantme to teach you to fight?\x03I thought you didn't care forviolence...\x03I do not like uncivilized behavior.\x03I think one can solve one's problemswithout fighting.\x03And yet...\x03	And yet what?\x03I've always relied on you toprotect me, Brother.\x03I would rather not be such aburden to you in the future.\x03So, I thought maybe I shouldlearn to protect myself...\x03	I'm your brother. Brothers aresupposed to protect their sisters.\x03It's nothing for you to worry about.It's no cause for concern.\x03Yes, but...\x03I am your sister. Sisters are supposedto worry about their brothers.\x03So I would like to learn something ofswordplay, if only a little.\x03And maybe, someday, I can protect youin your time of need...\x03So please, Ephraim.\x03	All right, all right. How could I say no?\x03Honestly, once you get an idea into yourhead, that's it. I might as well give in.\x03It's agreed. I'll teach you, but won'thold back because you're my sister.\x03And I want no complaining once we'vestarted, Eirika.\x03Complain? Me? Never!\x03";
