const char gCompressedText_MSG_0967[] = "		Hey, listen! My village isbeing attacked by bandits.\x03My name's Ross.\x03Come on! You have to helpme wipe those thugs out!\x03	All right, just... Just take adeep breath and calm down, Ross.\x03Leave the villages to us.We'll drive off the bandits.\x03Seth, take the boy somewhere safe.\x03No! Wait! I'm goingto fight, too!\x03	But...\x03My father is out there all alone,fighting those bandits.\x03I've got to get back to him asquickly as possible!\x03I'm the son of the great Garcia!\x03As long as I have my axe, nobandit will ever defeat me!\x03	All right, I can see you'renot going to be swayed...\x03But you must promise youwill stay close to us.\x03";
