const char gCompressedText_MSG_098B[] = "		The local villagers tell me thatBazba's Bandits keep their lair nearby.\x03A few of them saw a lad matching thedescription of our bracelet thief.\x03It seems a fair guess that the youthis one of these bandits.\x03Bandits... Here in Renais, our homeland.I had no idea...\x03Burning our villages... Stealing fromour people with no fear of reprisal?\x03	It wasn't always like this. The knightsused to protect the citizenry...\x03However, with Renais in ruins and her armytattered, law and order are hard to find.\x03It doesn't look like the Grado army isinterested in maintaining order here.\x03If nothing changes, Renais will continuethis sad plunge into savagery.\x03......\x03";
