const char gCompressedText_MSG_09BC[] = "	4KCaptain Saar of the Serafew BorderGuard. How fare you?\x03I bring orders from His Majesty.\x03Rumor has it that Princess Eirika ofRenais is making her way to Grado.\x03You are to find her and to placeher in custody immediately.\x03	Yes, sir!\x03One more thing...\x03A traitor to the empire has fledCastle Grado.\x03We've received reports she is hidingsomewhere here in Serafew.\x03I don't care if you have to tear thistown apart. Find the turncoat.\x03	Yes, sir, General Glen!\x03If she resists, do we havepermission to execute her?\x03...Yes. Permission granted.\x03	Understood! Grado's will be done.\x03The Grado Empire will repay thedebt of betrayal with blood!\x03...His Majesty relies upon you, Captain.Be sure his trust is not misplaced.\x03That is all.\x03	Yes, sir!\x03";
