const char gCompressedText_MSG_09BE[] = "		It's been so long since I lastvisited Serafew.\x03My brother and I used to passthrough here en route to Grado.\x03I remember the harmony in which thepeople of both countries lived.\x03No walls divided our borders. Nosoldiers stood guard in high towers.\x03This border town... It was to me a symbolof the trust between Grado and Renais.\x03...And now, it is firmly underthe thumb of Grado's emperor.\x03	The peace I remember in this city...\x03It seems like something from anothertime. It seems lost now... Forever.\x03...The city doesn't seem to be veryheavily patrolled.\x03They must feel it's not worth guardingwith Castle Renais under their control.\x03We must try to not draw attention toourselves. The west gate is undermanned...\x03 Pardon me, may I askyou a question?\x03	\n\nWhat is it?\x03I'm looking for someone.\x03Have you seen a young girlwith indigo hair?\x03Indigo hair?\x03No... Sorry.\x03Hmmm...\x03Thank you. Sorryto intrude.\x03";
