const char gCompressedText_MSG_09C9[] = "\n\nThat was a tight spot.\x03Yes, yes it was...Thank you so much.\x03I don't know how to repay--\x03You're from Grado, aren't you?\x03Yes...My name is Natasha.\x03I was a servant of the peopleat Grado's Imperial Temple.\x03\nThen why the trouble with the soldiers?Would you tell us your story?\x03Of course...\x03A few days past, my mentor was arrested without warning.\x03They executed him.They said he was a traitor...\x03But those were false accusations.\x03The emperor had him killed--a holyman!--to keep him silent.\x03Keep him silent?\x03Yes. My mentor told me withhis final breath.\x03The emperor plans to destroythe Sacred Stones.\x03\nThe Sacred Stones? Destroy them?\x03As you must know, the Sacred Stones droveback the power of evil long ago.\x03Even now, each of our nations is hometo one of these legendary treasures.\x03There's one in my homeland, Grado, andone in your Renais...\x03\nYes, the Sacred Stone of Renais isstill housed in our royal temple.\x03The emperor plans to destroy thefive stones, one by one...\x03Why would he do such a thing?\x03Legend says the Sacred Stones areeven now all that keeps evil at bay!\x03I cannot begin to guess his motives...\x03You must know, our emperor was a gentleman. But one day, he changed. Utterly.\x03Before my mentor died, he said the keepersof the Sacred Stones must be warned.\x03I tried to slip across the border, butthe soldiers spotted me...\x03\nIs that what happened...\x03What do you think, Seth?\x03I think we can trust no one from Grado.Not in these times. Not without proof.\x03However, if what she says is true, wecannot ignore the danger we face.\x03Destroying the Sacred Stones...We cannot allow that to happen.\x03\nI agree. If only we knew if there weresome reason for the emperor's actions.\x03I must tell you, her story chills me tothe bone. I pray it is false...\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_09CA[] = "\n...Ahh...\x03\nHold on! You must hold on!\x03Her wound is...\x03The...emp...emperor...\x03\nStop, you mustn't speak...\x03The emperor wants...de...\x03destroy...Sacred Stones...\x03What?!\x03\nDestroy the Sacred Stones?\x03Please...warn...\x03Protect the...five stones...\x03......\x03...She's dead.\x03\n......\x03Seth, what do you makeof her final words?\x03She said something about theSacred Stones.\x03She must have meant five stones thatbanished evil from Magvel long ago.\x03\nAnd the emperor--Grado's emperor?Is he trying to destroy them?\x03What does that mean?\x03I don't know.\x03If she had lived, we mighthave learned more, but...\x03\nDestroying the Sacred Stones...We cannot allow that to happen.\x03Could it really be true? What woulddrive the emperor to such madness?\x03I must tell you, her story chills meto the bone. I pray it is false.\x03 ";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_09CB[] = "	X	A moment, please.Are you perchance...\x03Princess Eirika?\x03I am.\x03	Oh... Thank goodness you're safe!I can't tell you how happy I am.\x03And please accept my gratitude fordriving off that Captain Saar.\x03That Saar treated all the citizens of Renaiswith such contempt and brutality...\x03Not here...not in this city.\x03My brother and I spent suchhappy times here with Lyon...\x03	I beg your pardon, but it will not belong before Grado sends more troops.\x03Please, you must go quickly.\x03I'm so sorry.\x03There's nothing I can do foryou now. Please forgive me.\x03	Do not be troubled.Princess Eirika...\x03We will survive and wait for theday of liberation to come.\x03There will come a day when you, PrinceEphraim, and all of Renais rise up...\x03Until that day of glory comes, we willwait unbowed and filled with hope.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_09CC[] = "	*	You... You're that man I met...\x03Are you here to capture me? You've beenhired to silence me, haven't you...\x03Yeah, Grado's paying the bill.They want you dead, you know?\x03But don't feel bad. It's not personal.\x03	Wait, please...\x03It doesn't matter what happens tome, but you must hear my words.\x03The emperor of Grado is changed.He is not the man he once was.\x03The other nations must be warned beforehe extinguishes all light from our lands.\x03Hey, no offense, but I'm just a mercenary.I don't care about Grado or its emperor.\x03Everything you say may be true, or it maybe lies. I don't care either way.\x03	But that's...\x03Even so... Killing a beautiful lady likeyou would leave a bad taste in my mouth.\x03Tell me, do you like to gamble?\x03	What?!\x03Gambling's what I live for. Evenwhen I lose, I never want to stop.\x03Let's have us a little wager.If you win, I'll believe you.\x03Heads or tails, you call it.\x03	You can't...This is no time for games...\x03Would you rather I get on with thejob I was hired for?\x03	......Um, heads...\x03No! Tails!\x03All right. So I'm heads,and you're tails.\x03Here we go.... ... ...\x03	......Which... Which is it?\x03What do you know?!\x03It's tails. You win. Figures.I haven't won anything all day.\x03Well, Lady Luck has spoken.Guess I'm on your side now.\x03	Are you serious?\x03Yeah. Sure, I might cheat, but I neverworm out of a bet. It's a rule of mine.\x03	Oh, thank heaven! Thank you, blessedlight, for your protection!\x03I got nothing against heaven, but I'm righthere if you want someone to thank...\x03No? Well, get behind me then. I'vegot to take care of these fools.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_09CD[] = "	X	Life in Serafew's been harder since theGrado occupation force took over here.\x03Serafew's got Renais citizens as well asGrado, but it's been hardest on us.\x03They've singled out families fromRenais for the most awful atrocities.\x03Please, traveler, take this sword.\x03It's an armorslayer. It'll cut througheven the strongest armor.\x03Take it and strike down thatblackheart, Saar.\x03";
const char gCompressedText_MSG_09CE[] = "		Oh, hello.Did you come to see me dance?\x03I'm sorry, but I just finished afew moments ago.\x03Oh, by the way... Would you be interestedin one of these items?\x03A wealthy patron left me a small ransomin gifts after watching my performance.\x03You can sell one for gold if you'd likeor use them to improve your skills.\x03I simply cannot carry all of this bymyself, so please, take this one.\x03Wealth is useless if you can't use itto bring happiness to others, right?\x03Thanks for dropping by. Perhaps we'llmeet again someday.\x03	";
