const char gCompressedText_MSG_0C59[] = "	\"Good day to you, Princess.\x03What a funny thing that we should meethere! It is providence, I tell you!\x03	L'Arachel, it is NOT providence.It is not even a coincidence.\x03We agreed to meet here when weplanned out our battle strategy.\x03Wait... Don't tell me that youdon't remember that!\x03We planned this?\x03I suppose I simply don't usuallyworry about such trifling details.\x03And here we are, so I suppose thatour plan must be working.\x03	I suppose you're right.\x03Still, divine providence or not,isn't it strange and wonderful?\x03A beautiful princess traveling withsuch a ragged bunch as this...\x03You could have told me much sooner,you know!\x03	My apologies.\x03Necessity demanded that I concealmy identity at the time.\x03Oh, it is no longer any worry.\x03To be honest, I believe I had figured outyour ruse from the very moment we met.\x03I said to myself, This lovely womancould only be of my own superior breeding.\x03After all, you could never truly foola woman with my keen mind.\x03	My. How...impressive.\x03There is something about nobility thatsimply cannot be hidden from its kin!\x03Why, Eirika, certainly you must havefelt the same thing upon seeing me?\x03You surely saw a refinement and grace ofcarriage surpassing that of common folk?\x03	Err... Aheh...\x03Yes, why...the very first timeI met you, I could see that you...\x03You were very far from common.\x03Exactly. Far from common. I couldnot have put it better myself.\x03It's simply impossible to travelincognito these days.\x03";
