const char gCompressedText_MSG_0C9C[] = "	\nNeimi. You seem to be adjustingto the rigors of combat well.\x03You're a skilled archer after all.\x03	Oh...I'm so glad to hear you say that!I was so sad after we talked last.\x03I didn't know what to do, but then,I decided to focus on my archery.\x03That's the spirit, Neimi. So, haveyou been training by yourself?\x03I never mastered archery. I'msorry I can't help you train.\x03	No, no... Thank you, but I'vebeen thinking about this a lot.\x03First, I need to sharpen my visionso I can target more easily.\x03Sharpen your vision?\x03Good eyesight seems essentialin a good archer, but...\x03How can you improve yourvision? I don't understand.\x03	My grandfather taught me to stareinto the distance and concentrate.\x03My grandfather taught me everythingI know about the bow.\x03My grandfather was--He was a great archer.\x03One time, a snake was attacking a bird nest on a tree in a mountain far away.\x03He aimed at the snake and shot it down.\x03Incredible. He was able to pick outand hit a snake from that distance?\x03Your grandfather must have beena great archer.\x03	Yes, he was. And that's why I'vebeen staring into the distance.\x03I've been training constantly on thefield, and my vision has improved.\x03See that tree in the distance? I canspot the bugs crawling on its leaves.\x03I'll be impressed when you canhit each of those bugs from here.\x03	But...that would be cruel!\x03There's no need to shoot bugs. Youonly need to shoot our enemies...\x03...using your keen eyes and theskills your grandfather gave you.\x03	Don't you worry!You can count on me!\x03";
