const char gCompressedText_MSG_0D1C[] = "		Hello, Marisa.\x03Chief.\x03	How're you doing? Your sword still sharp?\x03Same as always.\x03	You're not seriously injuredor ill, are you?\x03No.\x03	I see.So you can continue on?\x03Yes. Why all the questions?\x03	Oh.\x03I'm the commander, you know? I'm supposedto check on you now and then.\x03Well, see you later.\x03Wait.\x03	Hm?\x03I'd like you to keep talking.\x03I don't mind talking to you.\x03	You know, we've known each other for along time, so I understand you...\x03But listen, Marisa, it wouldn't hurtyou to be a bit more sociable.\x03Not for me, mind you, but some of theothers have a hard time working with you.\x03...\x03	Speaking of which, when I first metyou, you were always working alone.\x03I remember thinking how odd that was.\x03I figured a woman as beautiful and talentedas you would have men all around her.\x03Don't need 'em.\x03	You see, that's what I'm talking about!Your beauty belies your words.\x03Chief?\x03	Hm?\x03Do you like sociable women?\x03	Um...sure, I guess.I mean, doesn't everyone?\x03If you go to an inn, aren't thesociable gals the most popular?\x03I understand.OK. I'll be more sociable.\x03This better?\x03	Huh?!\x03";
