const char gCompressedText_MSG_0D1F[] = "	 Hello, Saleh!\x03	Gerik...\x03Imagine! You and me fighting together.Life's full of surprises, isn't it?\x03	I suppose so.\x03So, what do you think of our commander?\x03	I'm here.There's your answer.\x03Good point.\x03You know this job seems to have moremeaning than any of my previous ones.\x03And it's not because it deals with thecontinent and all the nations and all that.\x03I simply want to accomplish my employer'sgoals. That's my prime motivation.\x03	I think it will all work out.As long as you and I are here...\x03Ha ha ha! Well said.No one can touch us, is that it?\x03I do imagine with us in the fieldwe'll win most battles, eh?\x03Can't get overconfident, though.\x03	Mm.\x03......\x03Huh?What is it?\x03	Gerik...Do you...\x03Do I what?\x03	Nothing...Pay me no mind.\x03C'mon, now.What is it?\x03	Forgive me.It's nothing...\x03All right...Well then, let's get going.\x03When there's a break in the fighting,we should get together for a meal.\x03	Very well.\x03We'll eat to our mutual good fortune...\x03Yes, to luck!\x03";
