const char gCompressedText_MSG_0D37[] = "	\"#		Oh, I cannot believe it.\x03There is something verywrong with this world.\x03Hm?! What is it? What'shappened, Princess L'Arachel?\x03	Hello, Dozla.Listen to this.\x03The other day, I paid a visitto a nearby village.\x03I found something inconceivable there.\x03Not one of them had ever heard of thebeautiful banisher of darkness before.\x03What?!\x03Even with your anonymous campaignto rid the world of monstrosities?\x03I cannot fathom how those peoplecould be so uninformed!\x03	Last night, I was so distraught that Iquite nearly drowned my pillow in tears.\x03This will never do, Dozla.\x03I must be more famous. The entireworld must know of my legend.\x03The troubadours must be made tosing my praises far and wide.\x03And I'm sure they will!\x03	The five heroes who banished evil...\x03My own sacred ancestor...\x03Oh, to be like them... I so longto be praised by the masses, too.\x03Gwah ha ha!And you shall be, Princess!\x03	But I get the feeling that we're goingto have to change our methodology.\x03Appealing to the common people is ofthe utmost importance.\x03First and foremost, we need a plan ofaction. A means to win their hearts.\x03Please, Dozla, I want you tothink of something, too.\x03Gwah ha ha!Leave it to your trusted Dozla!\x03";
