const char gCompressedText_MSG_0D39[] = "	\"#	How is it progressing, Dozla?\x03Is it working?\x03Gwah ha ha!You will be pleased, Princess L'Arachel!\x03Just recently I saw a group ofvillagers together gossiping.\x03They'd seen a suspicious young woman infantastic garb riding around at night.\x03And they called that enigmatic woman thebeautiful princess of peerless beauty!\x03	Yes! They were most certainlytalking about me then.\x03At last, I am becoming known amongstthe people of the land.\x03Those three long trips I took aroundthe area were worth the trouble.\x03Gwah ha ha!You're so right, Princess L'Arachel!\x03There can be no doubt that thevillagers were appropriately impressed.\x03	Yet I find it passing strange.\x03How is it that no one hasappeared to imitate me?\x03The beautiful banisher of darknesswas well enough known, after all.\x03It's only natural that someone somewherewould have aspired to be like me.\x03The fact that no imitators have appearedhas me very worried, I must say.\x03Gwah ha ha!How right you are!\x03But you are peerless, Princess L'Arachel,as your nickname says!\x03It would be impossible for anyone toclaim your beauty as her own!\x03	Well, that is true. It certainly wasnot easy for me, after all.\x03Yet now, I am destined to beremembered in the future as a hero.\x03I wonder how my legend will be passed onafter I leave this earth.\x03I am so looking forward to it.\x03The beautiful princess of peerlessbeauty, L'Arachel...\x03Ah... How enchanting.\x03Already, I weep for the world thatwill one day be robbed of my beauty.\x03Gwah ha ha!\x03	I must do something spectacular thisbattle to ensure my name is remembered.\x03Let's go, Dozla.\x03Gwah ha ha! Ready as ever,Princess L'Arachel!\x03";
